name: Plug Punkz #004
description:
This is the O.G Collection of Plug Punkz, There will only be 25 Unique Designs.
2nd Generation will be a generative project of 400 each character.
By owning these original characters you are entitled to 1/3 plot of land in 'Plug Towers' which is the Metaverse based in PlugWorld.io
